 vocals {{small|(1995\u20131998)}}|drums, backing vocals {{small|(1998\u20132000)}}}}\n|{{hlist|''Warrant Live 86\u201397'' (1997)|''Greatest & Latest'' (1999)}}\n|-\n|{{CSS image crop |Image=Keri_Kelli.jpg |bSize=150 |cWidth=75 |cHeight=75 |oTop=25 |oLeft=55 }}\n|[[Keri Kelli]]\n|2000\n|lead and rhythm guitars\n|rowspan=\"5\"|none\n|-\n|\n|Shawn Zavodney\n|2001\u20132004\n|{{hlist|keyboards|backing vocals}}\n|-\n|\n|Dan Conway\n|2006\n|rowspan=\"2\"|drums\n|-\n|\n|[[Michael Foster (musician)|Michael Foster]]\n|2012\u20132013\n|-\n|\n|Kevin Baldes\n|2019\n|bass\n|\n|}\n\n==Timeline==\n{{#tag:timeline|\nImageSize = width:1000 height:auto barincrement:20\nPlotArea = left:100 bottom:100 top:05 right:20\nAlignbars = justify\nDateFormat = mm/dd/yyyy\nPeriod = from:06/01/1984 till:{{#time:m/d/Y}}\nTimeAxis = orientation:horizontal format:yyyy\nLegend     = orientation:vertical position:bottom columns:3\nScaleMajor = increment:2 start:1985\nScaleMinor = increment:1 start:1985\n\nColors =\n  id:vocals  value:red         legend:Lead_vocals\n  id:bvocals value:pink        legend:Backing_vocals\n  id:lguitar value:teal        legend:Lead_guitar\n  id:rguitar value:brightgreen legend:Rhythm_guitar\n  id:keys    value:purple      legend:Keyboards\n  id:bass    value:blue        legend:Bass\n  id:drums   value:orange      legend:Drums,_percussion\n  id:studio  value:black       legend:Studio_album\n  id:live    value:gray(0.7)   legend:Live_album\n  id:bars    value:gray(0.93)\n\nBackgroundColors = bars:bars\n\nLineData =\n layer:back\n color:live\n  at:07/25/1997\n color:studio\n  at:01/31/1989\n  at:09/11/1990\n  at:08/25/1992\n  at:03/07/1995\n  at:10/01/1996\n  at:10/05/1999\n  at:06/12/2001\n  at:06/27/2006\n  at:05/17/2011\n  at:05/12/2017\n\nBarData =\n  bar:Adam   text:\"Adam Shore\"\n  bar:Jani   text:\"Jani Lane\"\n  bar:Jaime  text:\"Jaime St. James\"\n  bar:Robert text:\"Robert Mason\"\n  bar:Josh   text:\"Josh Lewis\"\n  bar:Joey   text:\"Joey Allen\"\n  bar:Rick   t